oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Unnidentified young girl holding flowers
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The young girl in this image had long, dark hair, held back by a ribbon. Her light-colored dress was trimmed with dark ribbons extending down from either shoulder. Her cheeks were hand-tinted pink, as were the flowers that she clasped in her hands.; This image of an unidentified girl is from an old photograph album found at an estate sale.
